definitions.definition: The act of vending or selling; a sale .
( UK , Australia , dated ) The total sales of coal from a colliery .

main_definition: The act of vending or selling; a sale .

definitions.definition: The letter Ꝩ / ꝩ , used in Old Norse , related to the rune wynn ( ᚹ , whence also Latin-script Ƿ / ƿ ) but with the bowl open at the top, like a y .
